'''Hossam Abdelmageed Abdelsalam Abdelmegeed''' ({{langx|ar|حسام عبد المجيد عبد السلام عبد المجيد}}; born 30 April 2001) is an Egyptian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[centre-back]] for [[Egyptian Premier League]] club [[Zamalek SC|Zamalek]] and the [[Egypt national football team|Egypt national team]].<ref name="filgoal">{{cite web|url=https://www.filgoal.com/players/167538|title=FilGoal &#124; حسام عبد المجيد - لاعب نادي الزمالك|website=filgoal.com|accessdate=6 September 2020}}</ref><ref name="kooora">{{cite web|url=https://www.kooora.com/?player=154553|website=kooora.com|title=اللاعب: حسام عبد المجيد|accessdate=13 August 2024}}</ref><ref name="zamalek">{{cite web|url=https://zamalek.news/2020/09/كارتيرون-يكشف-سر-فوز-الزمالك-على-طلائع/|title=كارتيرون يكشف سر فوز الزمالك على طلائع الجيش - اخبار الزمالك|website=Zamalek News|accessdate=6 September 2020}}</ref>

==International career==

On 2 December 2025, Abdelmaguid was called up to the Egypt squad for the [[2025 Africa Cup of Nations]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cafonline.com/afcon2025/news/egypt-name-final-28-man-squad-for-totalenergies-caf-afcon-2025-salah-leads-pharaohs-charge/|title=Egypt name final 28-man squad for TotalEnergies CAF AFCON 2025, Salah leads Pharaohs' charge|publisher=[[Confederation of African Football]]|date=2 December 2025|access-date=12 December 2025}}</ref>

